Configuration > Discovery > Local Fields using Search and Facet Normalization Rules 
Add 
"Local Field 02"

Configuration > Discovery > Manage Display and Local Fields

Add field > Add local field

Field to edit: local_field_02

Display label: TEK-words / TEK-ord / TEK-ord

Enable field for search = YES
Enable field for facet = YES


NORMALISERINGSREGLER:

DISPLAY:

rule "Primo VE - Lds02"
	when
		MARC is "650"."a" AND
		MARC."650".ind"2" equals "7" AND
		MARC."650"."2" equals "tekord"
	then
		create pnx."display"."lds02" with MARC "650"."a"
end


SEARCH AND FACET:

rule "Primo VE Marc - Lsr02"
	when
		MARC is "650"."a" AND
		MARC."650".ind"2" equals "7" AND
		MARC."650"."2" equals "tekord"
	then
		create pnx."search"."lsr02" with MARC "650"."a"
end
